{"TopicId":150073,"ForumId":29,"TopicTitle":"Vector fonts","CreatedByName":"Teilnehmer","CreatedById":143330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-15T13:09:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Teilnehmer","CreatedById":143330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-15T13:09:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m using the \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003EUnityEngine.GUILayout\u003C/span\u003E controls with\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003EUnityEngine.GUI.skin\u003C/span\u003E style in my mod, and it looks like this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022CeowNIT.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/CeowNIT.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe fonts are raster.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I apply new KSP 1.2 vector fonts?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sarbian","CreatedById":57146,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-15T13:48:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can\u0027t with a GUILayour UI. You need a UI done with the modern UI Unity.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Teilnehmer","CreatedById":143330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-15T14:02:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOK, thanx!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Teilnehmer","CreatedById":143330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-16T05:37:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould you please give an example?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DMagic","CreatedById":57416,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-16T16:59:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf your mod just consists of the window shown above you can skip the tedious Unity stuff and just use the PopupDialog system:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/149324-popupdialog-and-the-dialoggui-classes/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt works similar to the GUILayout system but generates a UI using the new Unity UI system.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just added a more complex example of the\u00A0PopupDialog system used by my mod \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/108704-12-dmagics-modlets-all-the-updates-new-modlets-10-13-2016/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EScience Relay\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-16T17:11:02Z\u0022 title=\u002210/16/2016 05:11  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by DMagic\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}